31
00:01:15,484 --> 00:01:17,884
The company?

32
00:01:17,884 --> 00:01:20,084
Kudo, don't tell me that's...

33
00:01:20,084 --> 00:01:21,984
Yeah, I don't know if that "Company"

34
00:01:21,984 --> 00:01:23,684
is what we think it is

35
00:01:23,684 --> 00:01:26,084
or just any other company.

36
00:01:26,084 --> 00:01:27,484
But, the man told me that the old man

37
00:01:27,484 --> 00:01:28,884
really got along with that man,

38
00:01:28,884 --> 00:01:31,284
and that they used to have deep conversation with each other.

39
00:01:31,284 --> 00:01:34,684
Taking into consideration that he was an unmatched suspense fan,

40
00:01:34,684 --> 00:01:36,184
he figured from the way he talked

41
00:01:36,184 --> 00:01:39,184
or characteristic way of saying things...

42
00:01:39,184 --> 00:01:42,584
So he may be a member of "the Company"

43
00:01:42,584 --> 00:01:45,084
that we're thinking of.

44
00:01:45,084 --> 00:01:46,284
Yeah.

45
00:01:47,284 --> 00:01:48,684
But, Kudo,

46
00:01:48,684 --> 00:01:51,884
if it turns out to be true, it's big trouble.

47
00:01:51,884 --> 00:01:53,184
I think it's best to watch how things go

48
00:01:53,184 --> 00:01:55,284
without doing anything for now.

49
00:01:55,284 --> 00:01:57,984
What would you do?

50
