70
00:02:48,884 --> 00:02:51,284
Sorry, Hattori. I'll call you if I find out anything more.

71
00:02:51,284 --> 00:02:54,184
Hey, hold it.

72
00:02:57,884 --> 00:02:59,584
Be careful.

73
00:02:59,584 --> 00:03:00,984
Kudo.

74
00:03:14,084 --> 00:03:15,584
Sizzling hot suspense.

75
00:03:15,584 --> 00:03:18,084
A red scream and black bullet whizz through the darkness.

76
00:03:18,084 --> 00:03:19,884
Intertwined in the mystery of the Black Organization

77
00:03:19,884 --> 00:03:20,884
are Eisuke Hondo and Rena Mizunashi.

78
00:03:20,884 --> 00:03:23,684
The curtains of the new series are ready to unfold!

79
00:03:23,684 --> 00:03:25,184
He sees through the one and only truth.

80
00:03:25,184 --> 00:03:26,784
A child in appearance with the I.Q. of an adult.

81
00:03:26,784 --> 00:03:29,284
No case is left unsolved with Detective Conan.

82
00:04:54,377 --> 00:04:59,577
"Red and Black Crash: Prologue."

83
00:04:59,577 --> 00:05:01,677
"West Beika Hospital."

84
00:05:01,677 --> 00:05:04,377
Bye. See you!

85
00:05:05,977 --> 00:05:08,377
I tell you, that Aya.

86
00:05:08,377 --> 00:05:10,477
I mean we rush over super worried because we heard that

