00:05:17,777 --> 00:05:21,277
All for the better, since she seems to be doing great.

91
00:05:21,277 --> 00:05:24,877
Oh, no. Talking about food made my stomach growl.

92
00:05:24,877 --> 00:05:26,677
Let's go eat right now then!

93
00:05:26,677 --> 00:05:30,877
The burger shop that opened near here is pretty popular!

94
00:05:30,877 --> 00:05:32,377
Of course they also have

95
00:05:32,377 --> 00:05:35,877
the "children's set" that Conan loves too.

96
00:05:35,877 --> 00:05:38,177
It's the plate that comes with the toy.

97
00:05:38,177 --> 00:05:40,777
Then shall we invite him over to come too?

98
00:05:40,777 --> 00:05:41,877
Him?

99
00:05:41,877 --> 00:05:43,577
That klutz!

100
00:05:43,577 --> 00:05:45,577
Oh, Eisuke!

101
00:05:45,577 --> 00:05:47,377
Him!

102
00:05:47,377 --> 00:05:49,777
Oh, Ms. Mouri and Ms. Suzuki!

103
00:05:53,877 --> 00:05:55,377
I'm sorry.

104
00:05:55,377 --> 00:05:57,277
Hey, are you all right?

105
00:05:57,277 --> 00:05:59,077
Yes, somehow...

106
00:05:59,077 --> 00:06:01,777
What brings you all here?

107
00:06:01,777 --> 00:06:03,777
We went to visit a friend at the hospital.

108
00:06:03,777 --> 00:06:06,877
Don't tell me that he's come here because

109
00:06:06,877 --> 00:06:10,177
he's aware Rena Mizunashi is hospitalized somewhere?

110
00:06:13,977 --> 00:06:17,577
Isn't this Rena Mizunashi?

111
00:06:17,577 --> 00:06:20,377
You know, the popular announcer that's on leave now?

112
00:06:20,377 --> 00:06:21,377
You're right.

113
00:06:21,377 --> 00:06:23,377
She looks much younger than now, though...

114
00:06:23,377 --> 00:06:25,377
Oh, no,

115
00:06:25,377 --> 00:06:26,477
she's my older sister!

116
00:06:26,477 --> 00:06:28,077
Huh? Older sister?

117
00:06:28,077 --> 00:06:30,377
Not! You mean that announcer!

118
00:06:30,377 --> 00:06:33,377
No, although they look alike, they're not the same person.

119
00:06:33,377 --> 00:06:35,077
Their name's are different to

120
00:06:35,077 --> 00:06:38,277
and besides, my sister left home ten years ago.

121
00:06:38,277 --> 00:06:39,277
She left home?

122
00:06:39,277 --> 00:06:41,477
That's why I'm carrying this picture around

123
00:06:41,477 --> 00:06:42,977
and looking for her.

124
00:06:42,977 --> 00:06:45,877
But, why are you looking around hospitals?

125
00:06:45,877 --> 00:06:47,477
Sis used to always say that

126
00:06:47,477 --> 00:06:50,077
she wanted to be a nurse in the future.

127
00:06:50,077 --> 00:06:51,777
Besides, the hospital

128
00:06:51,777 --> 00:06:54,477
is the place where my sister saved me many times.

129
00:06:54,477 --> 00:06:57,277
I kind of feel that she's somewhere near hospitals.

130
00:06:57,277 --> 00:07:00,077
She saved you?

131
00:07:00,077 --> 00:07:02,677
I was a klutz since I was a child, and not only that,

132
00:07:02,677 --> 00:07:04,377
but also sickly,

133
00:07:04,377 --> 00:07:07,377
so sis used to take me to the hospital all the time.

134
00:07:07,377 --> 00:07:09,377
If I got hurt and bled, she would say,

135
00:07:09,377 --> 00:07:13,277
"You've got to take good care, because God blessed with blood"

136
00:07:13,277 --> 00:07:15,677
"that you can share with everybody else."

137
00:07:15,677 --> 00:07:17,377
But, on the contrary, it turned out that

138
00:07:17,377 --> 00:07:20,477
sis was the one who shared her blood with me.

139
00:07:20,477 --> 00:07:24,277
A little before sis disappeared, I was badly wounded...

140
00:07:31,177 --> 00:07:35,677
and I got a huge amount of blood transfusion from her.

141
00:07:35,677 --> 00:07:38,377
The blood flowing through my body

142
00:07:38,377 --> 00:07:40,277
is my sister's.

143
00:07:40,277 --> 00:07:45,777
I felt my sister's kindness each time my heart throbbed.

144
00:07:45,777 --> 00:07:47,977
However, when I was discharged from the hospital,

145
00:07:47,977 --> 00:07:49,777
my sister was gone.

146
00:07:49,777 --> 00:07:52,477
Maybe she thought that if she stuck around any longer,

147
00:07:52,477 --> 00:07:54,977
she would've had to give you all her blood.

148
00:07:54,977 --> 00:07:56,777
Hey, Sonoko!

149
00:07:56,777 --> 00:07:59,577
I have no idea why sis disappeared,

150
00:07:59,577 --> 00:08:00,677
but I want to see her one more time

151
00:08:00,677 --> 00:08:03,277
and tell her thank you from the bottom of my heart.

152
00:08:03,277 --> 00:08:06,877
After all, I'm alive now thanks to her.

153
00:08:06,877 --> 00:08:11,077
A blood type that can be given to anyone.

154
00:08:11,077 --> 00:08:15,377
What he just said doesn't sound like a lie.

155
00:08:15,377 --> 00:08:17,277
I guess it wouldn't be wrong to say

156
00:08:17,277 --> 00:08:20,477
he's looking for his older sister.

157
00:08:20,477 --> 00:08:23,777
That's just like us.

158
00:08:23,777 --> 00:08:28,777
Remember, some time back I gave you a lot of my blood too.

159
00:08:28,777 --> 00:08:31,377
Can you feel my kindness too?

160
00:08:31,377 --> 00:08:34,277
Yep. Sure thing...

161
00:08:34,277 --> 00:08:37,677
But, isn't there a chance that Rena Mizunashi

162
00:08:37,677 --> 00:08:39,877
and your older sister are one and the same?

163
00:08:39,877 --> 00:08:41,477
I don't think that's possible.

164
00:08:41,477 --> 00:08:42,677
Why not?

165
00:08:42,677 --> 00:08:46,377
If she's on TV, she may not be using her real name?

166
00:08:46,377 --> 00:08:47,977
Well, yes, but...

167
00:08:47,977 --> 00:08:49,477
Why don't we do this then?

168
00:08:49,477 --> 00:08:53,377
One of dad's friends is a great fan of Rena Mizunashi,

169
00:08:53,377 --> 00:08:56,677
and seems to have video taped her a lot.

170
00:08:56,677 --> 00:08:58,577
So, let's ask him to show them to us!

171
00:08:58,577 --> 00:09:00,577
If you take a good look at her, it may turn out that

172
00:09:00,577 --> 00:09:01,677
she's your older sister, right?

173
00:09:01,677 --> 00:09:02,977
I guess so.

174
00:09:02,977 --> 00:09:04,777
It's okay with me.

175
00:09:04,777 --> 00:09:07,577
Right, why don't we show that picture to him too?

176
00:09:07,577 --> 00:09:10,077
We may be able to find out if it's Rena Mizunashi.

177
00:09:10,077 --> 00:09:11,777
Okay.

178
00:09:13,977 --> 00:09:16,177
Yes, at any rate, let's head off.

179
00:09:16,177 --> 00:09:18,977
Before starting off, let's have lunch!

180
00:09:18,977 --> 00:09:20,277
Let's go.

