188
00:09:45,377 --> 00:09:47,277
No, it isn't!

189
00:09:47,777 --> 00:09:50,377
Oh no, I called the wrong number.

190
00:09:50,377 --> 00:09:51,877
Cool it.

191
00:09:51,877 --> 00:09:54,577
But if Eisuke's older sister

192
00:09:54,577 --> 00:09:56,277
is really Rena Mizunashi, that announcer,

193
00:09:56,277 --> 00:09:58,277
it's big news, you know.

194
00:10:00,777 --> 00:10:03,377
Oh, long time no talk, this is Ran Mouri.

